<h3 id="intersection-curves-of-surfaces-曲面的交线">Intersection curves of surfaces 曲面的交线</h3>
<ul>
  <li>conic intersection 锥面相交形成的建筑vault穹顶：
<img src="/images/posts/AG/vault.png" height="300" width="400" /></li>
</ul>

<blockquote>
  <p>If two rotational cylinders or cones possess a common inscribed sphere, their intersection curve decomposes into a pair of conic sections or into a conic section and a single ruling.</p>
</blockquote>

